query:
SELECT id, employee_id, course_id, confirmed_customers, course_fee, calculated_revenue, status, reviewed_by, reviewed_at 
FROM daily_stats 
WHERE status = 'approved' 
ORDER BY reviewed_at DESC 
LIMIT 5;
